{"tid":491354,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【連登戰報】連登網友幾乎一面倒睇好 港股有難？","createTime":"2017-12-06T12:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T12:39:14.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e5cb9b4933935bf107c52078001b3d5d20e03c52","tid":491354,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:25:21.000Z","msg":"【新增影片】<br />\n<br />\n今日港股一度大跌471點，今年升得多嘅吉利（175）、舜宇（2382）、瑞聲（2018）齊齊成為提款對象，急挫7%。有連登網友關心大市仲係咪牛市，估吓佢哋點睇？<br />\n開post的「有智慧不如趁勢」問：「究竟而家股市處於咩階段？」佢自己先答，認為未見雞犬升天狀態，冇大上大落過，感覺出年仲係大升市。有人回應：「3萬跌1500點好少咋喎」、「牛三前大震倉」、「跌完又升返啦」、「似上年，死完、又正常」、「每年升到咁上下，總會有調整，上山都要回下氣啦」，只有兩位網友話係熊一。換言之，有留言的連登網友，幾乎一面倒睇港股仲有得升。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171206/large/1512535427_3ffc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171206%2Flarge%2F1512535427_3ffc.jpg&h=de290b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171206/large/1512535428_ffe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171206%2Flarge%2F1512535428_ffe5.jpg&h=5a746954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171206/large/1512535430_7536.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171206%2Flarge%2F1512535430_7536.jpg&h=f9ac5bff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171206/57547190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57547190&d=UZhO%2BqJXOpLBLF1A1KKHvP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e45e9d67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57547190&h=440ce3e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171206/57547190</a><br />\n<br />\n//連登財經台巴打威到上新聞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f10d36db09cde92e3e8e8378fbe1ba99ccc1dd","tid":491354,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:26:37.000Z","msg":"毒果咁都可以當新聞?<br />\n<br />\n淡友講野又唔cap?<br />\n<br />\n唔好搵波台黎笑? 邊場波都有人嬴有人輸嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母毒果"},{"pid":"acfe2e75a5b5e1e67b429fa41dfb067a16f167d8","tid":491354,"uid":98659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:37:55.000Z","msg":"D記者咁撚得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5041ae66786c381bd5dd32aaf31284e337430a5a","tid":491354,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:39:14.000Z","msg":"hea工<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}